WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.275
=Episode 23=

00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:55.640
Come on, Aoxue.

00:00:56.290 --> 00:00:57.359
- Eat more.
- Thanks, Dad.

00:01:02.159 --> 00:01:02.960
Dad.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:05.320
You're back.

00:01:07.039 --> 00:01:07.840
Is there

00:01:08.119 --> 00:01:09.359
any good news today?

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:10.760
Aodong, didn't you see?

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:12.600
Ohara Pharma
is holding a press conference,

00:01:12.610 --> 00:01:14.800
accusing our family
of stealing their patented formula.

00:01:15.159 --> 00:01:15.719
Yes.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.500
I've been worrying about that, Dad.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:19.120
I'm really worried.

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:21.560
Given Ichiro Ohara's usual style,

00:01:22.125 --> 00:01:24.862
he wouldn't be this confident

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.190
unless he had already obtained
our Ninefold True Essence Pill formula.

00:01:27.837 --> 00:01:29.959
Dad, if things are that serious,

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.680
why are we still sitting here eating?

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:34.725
No matter how or through whom

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.825
Ichiro Ohara obtained that formula,

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.120
it's fake.

00:01:39.599 --> 00:01:40.120
Fake?

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:40.560
Yes.

00:01:42.599 --> 00:01:43.799
Dong, come here.

00:01:47.239 --> 00:01:49.280
There's only one real formula.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:52.575
And it's been locked in the safe
in my office this whole time.

00:01:55.079 --> 00:01:55.400
Come.

00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:56.840
Sit down and eat.

00:01:58.660 --> 00:01:59.239
Go ahead, sit.

00:01:59.239 --> 00:01:59.879
I'll sit.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:01.719
Aodong,

00:02:02.359 --> 00:02:03.640
do you know what Dad calls this?

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:04.890
Turning their plan against them.

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:06.990
Let that Ichiro Ohara show off first,

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.439
then at the press conference,

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:09.518
we'll expose him on the spot

00:02:09.519 --> 00:02:10.790
and see if he still dares
to act so arrogant.

00:02:13.079 --> 00:02:14.159
Do you still remember

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.280
what I always teach you two?

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:17.560
Of course we do.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.120
Dad, you always say,

00:02:19.300 --> 00:02:20.479
even though we're businessmen,

00:02:20.612 --> 00:02:22.840
we shouldn't only care about money.

00:02:23.912 --> 00:02:24.560
Well said.

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:27.639
This time, if the Ninefold
True Essence Pill formula

00:02:27.950 --> 00:02:30.039
really gets stolen by those Japanese,

00:02:30.530 --> 00:02:32.400
the Qin family's loss
would be the least of it.

00:02:33.162 --> 00:02:35.114
The nation's loss would be far greater.

00:02:36.612 --> 00:02:38.259
We would be letting down our ancestors

00:02:39.350 --> 00:02:40.517
and our nation.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:43.680
Do you both understand

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:45.639
the gravity of this matter?

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:48.800
Dong?

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.039
Dad.

00:02:50.719 --> 00:02:51.680
I understand.

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:53.680
Your teachings

00:02:54.199 --> 00:02:55.240
are always in my heart.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.360
Come.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.240
Let's cheers.

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:02.719
Alright.

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:05.520
Here, Dad.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:40.840
Dad!

00:03:41.270 --> 00:03:42.240
Dad, please listen to me!

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:42.599
I...

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:43.479
Dad!

00:03:44.039 --> 00:03:45.000
You piece of trash!

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:46.270
Dad, please don't be angry first!

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:47.400
Dad, I didn't want to do this too!

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.280
Someone forced me to do it!

00:03:48.280 --> 00:03:50.039
Didn't I make myself clear before?

00:03:50.040 --> 00:03:51.790
How could you still do something
like this?!

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:53.000
Listen to me.

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.280
This is the only bad thing
I've ever done!

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.240
I haven't done anything else!

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:56.639
Guards!

00:03:56.639 --> 00:03:57.550
I just had a moment of weakness!

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.680
Take him back home.

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:00.080
Interrogate him properly!

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.360
No, Dad! I'll punish myself!

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:02.919
Please don't be angry!

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:03.560
Don't be angry!

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:04.719
Dad, I was wrong!

00:04:04.719 --> 00:04:06.319
Dad, I was really wrong!

00:04:06.319 --> 00:04:06.879
Dad!

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:08.280
I was wrong. Please listen to me!

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:08.919
I'm sorry. Dad!

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:10.280
Dad!

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:12.039
Mr. Qin,

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:14.879
I think questioning Qin Aodong
can wait for now.

00:04:15.510 --> 00:04:16.560
What matters most right now

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:18.380
is figuring out how
to deal with Ohara Pharma.

00:04:22.439 --> 00:04:24.079
Welcome, everyone

00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:26.439
(Press Conference)
to today's press conference

00:04:27.012 --> 00:04:28.439
Ohara Pharma

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:30.759
has always believed
in harmony above all.

00:04:31.079 --> 00:04:32.399
But that doesn't mean

00:04:32.537 --> 00:04:34.945
(Ohara Ohara. Chairman of Ohara Pharma)
we can be bullied at will.

00:04:35.879 --> 00:04:36.360
However,

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:39.480
Huaying Pharma's
Ninefold True Essence Pill

00:04:39.879 --> 00:04:42.000
has blatantly plagiarized
our Shinbu Pill.

00:04:42.519 --> 00:04:43.519
Such behavior

00:04:43.519 --> 00:04:45.000
is absolutely unacceptable.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.360
Our domestic pharmaceutical company
actually copied a foreign product?

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:50.120
Everyone, please look at the screen.

00:04:50.862 --> 00:04:51.600
(Shinbu Pill)
On this side

00:04:51.839 --> 00:04:53.360
(Ninefold True Essence Pill)
is the formula for Shinbu Pill.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:54.920
Ten years ago,

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.959
we already registered the patent for it.

00:04:57.012 --> 00:04:58.319
(Hongwu: We got him.)

00:04:58.319 --> 00:05:01.160
And here is the formula
for Ninefold True Essence Pill .

00:05:01.662 --> 00:05:03.680
(Wang Daokun: The screen is connected.)
They're using the same ingredients!

00:05:03.700 --> 00:05:04.920
Aren't these exactly the same?

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:05.839
That's solid proof.

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:08.000
Mr. Ohara, may I ask

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:11.279
how you obtained the formula
for Ninefold True Essence Pill?

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:12.839
It was provided to me

00:05:13.079 --> 00:05:14.399
by a righteous insider

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.279
who simply could not tolerate

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.759
Huaying Pharma's

00:05:17.912 --> 00:05:20.833
blatant lack

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.959
of business ethics.

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:24.639
You thief.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:27.439
How dare you stand here

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.519
talking about justice?

00:05:30.279 --> 00:05:30.839
Mr. Ye,

00:05:31.487 --> 00:05:33.687
making false accusations
can carry legal consequences.

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:36.279
Your Shinbu Pill

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:38.160
and the Ninefold True Essence Pill

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:39.879
both originate

00:05:40.180 --> 00:05:41.360
from the same ancient formula.

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:44.480
Moreover, both are incomplete versions.

00:05:45.519 --> 00:05:46.639
But the only difference is,

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:47.920
you

00:05:48.959 --> 00:05:49.600
stole yours.

00:05:56.199 --> 00:05:57.040
Everyone, please look.

00:05:57.500 --> 00:05:59.062
This is the ancient formula I mentioned.

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:00.920
See if you can spot the difference.

00:06:00.959 --> 00:06:02.439
Does it look different?

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:04.040
Yes.

00:06:04.387 --> 00:06:06.113
Although they use the same herbs,

00:06:06.300 --> 00:06:08.690
the dosages and ratios
of several ingredients are different.

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:10.480
Today, I've specially invited

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.600
the most authoritative
third-party testing agency,

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:15.225
along with the most advanced
pharmaceutical testing equipment.

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:16.990
We'll conduct the test right here
on the spot.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:20.590
Today, I'll personally brew
a medicinal decoction.

00:06:20.660 --> 00:06:22.079
Then we'll have the inspection team

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:24.560
perform the most fair
and impartial verification.

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:26.199
- Good!
- Alright!

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:28.160
Everyone, please quiet down.

00:06:28.639 --> 00:06:29.319
I don't think

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:31.079
there's any need

00:06:31.079 --> 00:06:32.639
to waste everyone's valuable time.

00:06:34.362 --> 00:06:36.639
Do you all want to see this play out?

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:37.439
- Yes!
- Yes!

00:06:37.439 --> 00:06:39.759
Let's brew the medicine here
and prove which one's real!

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:41.639
- Yes!
- Yes!

00:06:41.850 --> 00:06:44.399
The third-party testing credentials
have already been verified.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.800
(Certification of Qualification)
There's no issue.

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:48.360
Bring in the herbs.

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.480
Master, good luck!

00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:00.790
Just sit back and enjoy the show.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:43.199
I will now read out the test results.

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:45.480
The composition
of the medicinal decoction

00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:46.639
just prepared by Mr. Ye Chen

00:07:46.639 --> 00:07:49.240
fully matches the ancient formula
he submitted.

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:51.800
As for its therapeutic effects,

00:07:52.375 --> 00:07:55.101
they are identical

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.639
to Ohara Pharma's Shinbu Pill

00:07:57.650 --> 00:07:58.990
and Huaying Phama's
Ninefold True Essence Pill .

00:08:00.279 --> 00:08:01.000
However,

00:08:02.079 --> 00:08:04.560
its potency is ten times stronger
than the other two.

00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:11.990
When the apprentice meets the master,

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:14.120
your little tricks

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:15.839
won't hold up.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.600
This is nothing but coincidence!

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.399
Our patent predates yours.

00:08:19.759 --> 00:08:20.879
We're the rightful creators.

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:22.959
The one I'm talking about is you!

00:08:23.279 --> 00:08:23.639
You!

00:08:23.839 --> 00:08:25.879
You stole an ancient formula
from our country,

00:08:26.079 --> 00:08:27.319
rushed to patent it first,

00:08:27.500 --> 00:08:29.150
and used it to crush our pharma industry.

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:31.040
You're the real joke here.

00:08:31.639 --> 00:08:32.839
And that's not the only formula

00:08:33.319 --> 00:08:34.600
he stole.

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:36.475
Baoyuan Hall's Vitality Pill,

00:08:36.637 --> 00:08:38.329
Yixin Pharma's Calmheart Powder,

00:08:38.710 --> 00:08:40.360
and Changsheng Pharma's
Revival Ointment.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.360
They stole them all using the same trick.

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:44.120
They pulled today.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:45.799
- How can this be?
- Exactly!

00:08:45.799 --> 00:08:47.280
You're making outrageous accusations.

00:08:47.799 --> 00:08:49.159
Aren't you afraid I'll sue you?

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:51.120
Still trying to deny it?

00:08:51.759 --> 00:08:53.279
Every formula you stole

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.240
came from

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:57.360
an ancient Chinese medical compendium.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:01.600
And that book must have been passed down
from your grandfather, right?

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:04.840
You have a grandfather,

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.519
and so do I.

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:09.660
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:09:09.790 --> 00:09:11.440
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:13.000
(Qingnang Manuscript Fragment)

00:09:13.010 --> 00:09:14.520
Take a look. Do you know what this is?

00:09:15.960 --> 00:09:17.039
Impossible!

00:09:17.550 --> 00:09:19.758
My grandfather said
this book was already lost.

00:09:20.279 --> 00:09:22.000
He said he was the only one
who had a copy.

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:24.120
He admitted it!

00:09:26.159 --> 00:09:27.080
He stole it!

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:28.000
Shameless!

00:09:28.559 --> 00:09:29.519
Let me ask you again.

00:09:30.075 --> 00:09:32.362
How did the copy of this book end up

00:09:32.570 --> 00:09:33.720
in your grandfather's hands?

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:37.200
You don't dare say it, do you?

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:38.519
Fine.

00:09:39.679 --> 00:09:40.559
I'll say it for you.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:43.000
Your grandfather was a bandit.

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:46.025
He snatched it from our ancestors.

00:09:46.799 --> 00:09:47.440
That old man

00:09:47.812 --> 00:09:49.855
is the founder of Ohara Pharma.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:53.039
He was also once

00:09:53.039 --> 00:09:54.879
a member of notorious unit!

00:09:55.399 --> 00:09:56.159
(Yoshio Ohara, Founder of Ohara Pharma)
Piece of trash!

00:09:56.159 --> 00:09:58.200
He stole our stuff
and now he's accusing us!

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:59.759
Exactly! A thief crying "thief"?!

00:09:59.759 --> 00:10:00.919
Shameless!

00:10:00.919 --> 00:10:01.600
Thief!

00:10:01.879 --> 00:10:03.240
- Thief!
- Thief!

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:04.639
Thief!

00:10:05.700 --> 00:10:07.280
But your grandfather didn't lie to you.

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:08.700
This Qingnang Manuscript Fragment

00:10:09.519 --> 00:10:10.799
was indeed lost.

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:12.240
And this copy

00:10:13.159 --> 00:10:15.720
was reconstructed by my grandfather
from ancient prescriptions

00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:17.559
scattered among the people.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.120
Is that clear enough?

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:22.919
Today's press conference

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:24.639
is over.

00:10:25.039 --> 00:10:25.679
After this,

00:10:26.039 --> 00:10:27.320
I will give everyone

00:10:27.559 --> 00:10:28.480
a full explanation.

00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:30.390
You think you can just say it's over
and walk away?

00:10:31.480 --> 00:10:32.820
You bribed Liu Baoliang,

00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:34.679
the production manager
of Huaying Pharma,

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:37.039
to replace notoginseng
with false notoginseng.

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.279
That caused

00:10:39.279 --> 00:10:41.000
immeasurable losses to Huaying Pharma.

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:42.519
What about the patients

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:45.080
still in the hospital?

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:46.960
How are you going

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:48.519
to account for that?

00:10:51.159 --> 00:10:52.087
What you're saying

00:10:52.879 --> 00:10:53.960
requires evidence.

00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:54.960
I have a witness!

00:10:57.100 --> 00:10:58.120
- Let me go!
- Walk!

00:10:58.437 --> 00:11:03.762
♪Bow to the flames.
The King of Ashes is me♪

00:11:07.399 --> 00:11:08.200
Don't run!

00:11:11.037 --> 00:11:12.950
♪I am the light♪

00:11:13.062 --> 00:11:15.637
♪The wind blows through the streets
that once denied me♪

00:11:15.679 --> 00:11:16.480
Get over there!

00:11:18.740 --> 00:11:19.320
Tell the truth.

00:11:19.639 --> 00:11:22.799
I was framed!

00:11:22.887 --> 00:11:24.564
Qin Aodong was the one who connected us.

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:26.080
And then

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:27.919
he gave my son 50 million
in cryptocurrency

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:29.850
to swap the notoginseng
with false notoginseng.

00:11:30.360 --> 00:11:32.200
I didn't want to do it!

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:34.120
They forced me!

00:11:34.175 --> 00:11:35.500
How did they force you?

00:11:35.912 --> 00:11:36.519
Well...

00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:39.000
I made a kind of incense for him.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:40.840
Then he mixed datura

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:41.612
into it.

00:11:44.039 --> 00:11:45.039
This is outrageous!

00:11:45.039 --> 00:11:45.919
Unbelievable.

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.080
Dad,

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:50.000
please calm down first.

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:52.120
Qin Aodong also threatened me

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:53.919
that if I didn't cooperate,

00:11:54.519 --> 00:11:56.000
he'd report everything to Mr. Qin.

00:11:56.120 --> 00:11:57.840
Then we'd all be finished.

00:12:03.262 --> 00:12:05.460
(Shinbu Pill VS
Ninefold True Essence Pill)

00:12:05.460 --> 00:12:07.612
(Press Conference Check-in Desk)

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.679
No wonder we couldn't find anything.

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.790
An inside job is the hardest
to guard against.

00:12:31.679 --> 00:12:33.840
So it really was you who poisoned Aoxue!

00:12:35.080 --> 00:12:35.879
Yes, it was me.

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:39.639
Why would you do this?

00:12:39.879 --> 00:12:40.679
Why?

00:12:42.639 --> 00:12:43.440
Why?

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.519
Why, why, why?

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:46.519
Why?

00:12:47.639 --> 00:12:49.039
Other than beating and scolding me,

00:12:49.400 --> 00:12:51.190
have you ever even touched
a finger of Aoxue?

00:12:51.237 --> 00:12:52.518
Have you ever scolded her once?

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:54.840
She's your sister.

00:12:55.759 --> 00:12:57.480
And she's a girl!

00:12:58.300 --> 00:12:59.990
What's wrong
with me treating her a little better?

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:01.759
Did I do something wrong as her father?

00:13:02.399 --> 00:13:03.440
I heard everything.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:05.450
You wanted
to leave the family fortune to her!

00:13:05.780 --> 00:13:07.600
And let someone
like him take advantage of it?

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:08.799
I'm your son, Dad!

00:13:08.799 --> 00:13:09.840
Your son!

00:13:09.840 --> 00:13:11.200
You should be giving it to me!

00:13:11.350 --> 00:13:13.759
I only wanted to poison her
till she turned stupid and mute.

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.360
You're the one who ruined my plan!

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:16.480
Do you know that, Ye Chen?

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:17.720
It's all because of you!

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:19.159
You forced me into this!

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:20.799
And you still think you're innocent?

00:13:21.039 --> 00:13:22.440
If I can't have it, I'll destroy it.

00:13:22.759 --> 00:13:24.080
No one else will get it either!

00:13:24.799 --> 00:13:26.960
Even if I handed Huaying over
to you now,

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:29.159
could you even manage it?

00:13:29.650 --> 00:13:32.851
Do you really think you're capable?

00:13:34.360 --> 00:13:34.960
Dad,

00:13:35.559 --> 00:13:37.639
whether I'm capable
or not isn't the point.

00:13:37.639 --> 00:13:38.279
Do you know what the point is?

00:13:38.279 --> 00:13:39.637
The point is I want it!

00:13:40.360 --> 00:13:41.879
And no one can take it from me.

00:13:46.399 --> 00:13:48.039
You're my son.

00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:51.159
Did you really think
I wouldn't look after you?

00:13:52.519 --> 00:13:54.759
I already set up
a five-billion trust fund

00:13:54.759 --> 00:13:56.200
in your name at the bank.

00:13:56.520 --> 00:13:57.580
That's enough for you

00:13:57.580 --> 00:13:59.920
to live comfortably
for the rest of your life!

00:14:00.879 --> 00:14:01.759
Five billion?

00:14:02.799 --> 00:14:03.600
You...

00:14:10.360 --> 00:14:10.960
Dad.

00:14:11.960 --> 00:14:12.600
Dad.

00:14:13.159 --> 00:14:14.360
I was wrong!

00:14:14.799 --> 00:14:15.600
I'll change!

00:14:16.080 --> 00:14:17.279
I swear I'll change, Dad!

00:14:17.639 --> 00:14:18.679
I'll change, I will!

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:19.960
Okay, Dad?

00:14:20.260 --> 00:14:21.200
Dad, please forgive me.

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:21.720
Dad!

00:14:27.559 --> 00:14:28.159
Dad.

00:14:31.799 --> 00:14:32.639
Guards.

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:37.679
Take him to the police station.

00:14:38.039 --> 00:14:39.879
Handle it according to the law.

00:14:40.519 --> 00:14:41.240
Yes, sir.

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:42.440
Dad!

00:14:42.500 --> 00:14:43.960
Dad, just listen to me one more time!

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:45.639
You're no match for Ichiro Ohara!

00:14:45.639 --> 00:14:46.240
Dad!

00:14:46.840 --> 00:14:47.240
Dad!

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:48.159
I was wrong!

00:14:49.919 --> 00:14:50.480
Dad!

00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:52.320
Dad!

00:14:55.679 --> 00:14:56.960
You mean,

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:58.919
someone was after the formula,

00:14:59.060 --> 00:15:01.080
so they caused the accident
that killed my parents?

00:15:01.799 --> 00:15:04.600
Tang Sihai was originally
your father's personal steward.

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:07.360
But one year
before your father's accident,

00:15:07.437 --> 00:15:09.077
the two of them had a huge argument

00:15:09.077 --> 00:15:11.038
and never contacted
each other again ever since.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.679
Are you suspecting Tang Sihai?

00:15:32.812 --> 00:15:35.300
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:15:35.387 --> 00:15:39.140
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:44.537
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:15:44.700 --> 00:15:46.987
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:15:47.300 --> 00:15:49.980
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:15:51.050 --> 00:15:53.675
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:15:53.975 --> 00:15:56.987
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:15:57.187 --> 00:16:00.237
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:16:00.350 --> 00:16:03.312
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:16:03.580 --> 00:16:06.737
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:16:06.962 --> 00:16:10.712
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:16:10.712 --> 00:16:13.575
♪I belong to no one♪

00:16:13.637 --> 00:16:17.087
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:16:17.087 --> 00:16:19.762
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:16:19.762 --> 00:16:26.100
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪